Uses of Package
com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb

Packages that use com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb
com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb This package contains the interfaces for the databases and loaders. 
com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb.db This package and its sub-packages contains the classes that implement database descriptors. 
com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb.db.derby This package contains the classes that implement the support for Apache Derby. 
com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb.db.hsqldb This package contains the classes that implement the support for HSQLDB. 
com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb.ldr This package contains the classes that implement the loaders. 
com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb.ldr.dbunit This package contains the classes that implement the loaders for DBUnit data sets. 
com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb.ldr.sqltool This package contains the classes that implement the loaders for DDL/DML scripts. 
com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb.mojo This package contains the classes that implement the plug-in's Mojos. 
 

Classes in com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb used by com.btmatthews.maven.plugins.inmemdb
Database
          Describes the operations that are used by the Mojos to launch in-memory databases, load data into, execute scripts against or shutdown the database.
Logger
          The interface that must be implemented by the object that logs messages to the Maven log file.
